    <introduction>
    </introduction>

    <section address="summary">
      <content>
        <para>
          This package includes two classes that include boilerplate code for implementing
          Docker container or Kubernetes service applications, including integrated logging
          as well as handling termination signals for Linux and OS/X.  These classes also
          provide a nice way to unit test your services.
        </para>
        <para>
          <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false">T:Neon.Service.KubeService</codeEntityReference> can be
          used as the base class for your service.
        </para>
        <para>
          <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false">T:Neon.Service.ProcessTerminator</codeEntityReference>
          is a lower-level class that receives and handle Linux and OS/X termination signals.
        </para>
      </content>
    </section>

